3.12	Andrea_Tafi_(cyclist)	Andrea Tafi (cyclist)	Andrea Tafi (born 7 May 1966 in Fucecchio) is an Italian former road bicycle racer who retired from his professional career in 2005. Tafi's propensity to perform best in the harder races earned him the nickname Il Gladiatore (The Gladiator).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a0/Andr%C3%A9a_TAFI.jpg/220px-Andr%C3%A9a_TAFI.jpg
